00:56.014 --> 00:57.057
‐ I wasn't thinking, okay?

00:57.057 --> 00:58.809
It just‐‐
ISABEL: I am trying so hard

00:58.809 --> 01:00.060
to wrap my head around all of this,

01:00.060 --> 01:01.603
and you go and‐‐
‐ I'm sorry!

01:01.603 --> 01:03.480
It's just‐‐
‐ It's just what?

01:03.480 --> 01:05.607
What excuse

01:05.607 --> 01:08.277
