for doing that in my house?

01:08.277 --> 01:10.404
‐ What do you mean by "that?"

01:10.404 --> 01:11.989
‐ Benji, please.

01:13.198 --> 01:16.535
‐ I mean having sex
with Adrian in the next room.

01:16.535 --> 01:19.162
‐ Oh, sex, or gay sex?
‐ Stop!

01:19.162 --> 01:21.915
‐ Look, that was awkward for all of us.

01:21.915 --> 01:24.209
But we're in a serious relationship.

01:24.209 --> 01:25.878
