of Doritos

04:51.124 --> 04:52.459
and third hour of Family Feud.

04:52.459 --> 04:56.171
‐ Oh. That explains the
Steve Harvey nightmare.

04:56.171 --> 04:58.841
He refused to crown me Miss Universe.

04:58.841 --> 05:00.634
