[phone vibrates]

05:05.764 --> 05:07.599
‐ You okay?

05:07.599 --> 05:10.477
‐ Yeah. Yeah, no, it's, um,

05:10.477 --> 05:12.980
um, my mom wants me to visit her

05:12.980 --> 05:14.815
at the hospital after school today.

05:14.815 --> 05:18.443
‐ That's good news, right?
‐ Yeah.

05:18.443 --> 05:21.613
Yeah, no, I‐‐ I guess. It's just, um,

05:21.613 --> 05:24.074
