05:24.074 --> 05:26.493
‐ A few days ago your mom
didn't want to see anyone,

05:26.493 --> 05:28.912
and now she's asking you to visit.

05:28.912 --> 05:30.539
I think that's a good sign.

05:34.376 --> 05:37.045
‐ Hey, you know, um...

05:37.045 --> 05:42.593
