finish out your semester.

07:17.938 --> 07:20.274
Now, if I take this,

07:20.274 --> 07:24.111
I really want to know how you feel. Okay?

07:24.111 --> 07:26.488
Because you know me. I'm Mr. Neutral.

07:26.488 --> 07:27.698
